# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and working tree, so tooling
# (Biome, etc.) behaves the same on Windows and CI. Without this, Windows
# checkouts with core.autocrlf=true get CRLF and `npm run lint` reports every
# file as a format error even though CI (LF) is clean.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be normalized.
*.svg text eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
